{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:15:42.073359+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I now have all the information needed. Here's the summary:\n\n---\n\n## NPM Scripts Summary for `T02_R02_C03_A03`\n\nThis is a **Create React App (CRA) template** (`cra-template-firebase-starter`), so there are two sets of scripts:\n\n### Root `package.json` (template repository — for template authors)\n\n| Script | Command | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `start` | `react-scripts start` | Local dev server with hot-reload |\n| `build` | `react-scripts build` | Production build |\n| `test` | `react-scripts test` | Runs tests (Jest) |\n| `eject` | `react-scripts eject` | Eject from CRA |\n| `predeploy` | `npm run build` | Auto-runs build before deploy |\n| `deploy` | `gh-pages -d build` | Deploys to GitHub Pages |\n| `clean-files` | `rm -rf ./template/public ./template/src` | Cleans the template directory |\n| `copy-files` | `cp -a ./src/. template/src && cp -a ./public/. template/public` | Syncs root source into `template/` |\n| `prepublishOnly` | `npm run clean-files && npm run copy-files` | Prepares the template for npm publish |\n\n### `template.json` (installed into user's project via `create-react-app --template`)\n\n| Script | Command | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `start` | `react-scripts start` | Local dev server |\n| `build` | `react-scripts build` | Production build |\n| `build-and-serve` | `npm run build && npm run serve` | **Build then serve locally** |\n| `serve` | `serve -s build` | Serve the production build directory |\n| `test` | `react-scripts test` | Runs tests |\n| `eject` | `react-scripts eject` | Eject from CRA |\n| `predeploy` | `npm run build` | Auto-runs build before deploy |\n| `deploy` | `gh-pages -d build` | Deploys to GitHub Pages |\n| `pull` | `git pull && npm i && npm start` | Pull latest, install, and start dev server |\n\n---\n\n## Testing a Production Build Locally Before Publishing\n\nThe README (step 3 under \"To Deploy on G